      <img
        src="{{ 'rating-stars.svg' | asset_url }}"
        alt="★★★★★"
        width="90"
        height="18">
      <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 my-0 mt-3">
        Discover why 10,000+ people worldwide trust TryScent                                    
        to keep them smelling unforgettable.
        <p>(Our customers were provided with a token of appreciation for sharing their stories with us)</p>
      </p>
    </div>
